ww.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/mechabop-peace-sign-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Team TriGear 的<em>Mechabop</em>是一款色彩缤纷的卡通 Roguelike 节奏射击游戏，其灵感来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/hades"><em>《Hades》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/jet-set-radio"><em>《Jet Set Radio》</em></a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/the-future-of-games-done-quick-why-founder-mike-uyamas-exit-is-on-hold-and-whats-next-3490793">Games Done Quick 的未来：为什么创始人 Mike Uyama 的退出被搁置，以及下一步是什么</a></strong></li></ul><p>从视觉上看，它与后一个游戏非常相似，还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/bomb-rush-cyberpunk"><em>《Bomb Rush Cyber​​punk》</em></a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/hi-fi-rush"><em>《Hi-Fi Rush》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/neon-white"><em>《Neon White》</em></a> 。这种低多边形艺术方向适合<em>Mechabop</em>向玩家介绍的明亮的漫画风格城市。</p><p>机器人敌人也会对可玩主角的名字“雨”做出反应。 Flipside 是一种坦克型的格斗者，在受到攻击时<a href="https://twitter.com/TeamTriGear/status/1686768827449614336" target="_blank" rel="noopener">，它的傻笑会变成冷酷的鬼脸</a>。</p><p>或者，<a href="https://twitter.com/TeamTriGear/status/1668649430289899520" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MORT</a>会小跑穿过各个关卡，直到受到威胁，它会通过变成发射导弹的炮塔来做出反应。幸运的是，玩家能够在精确的时刻抛出和平标志，将敌人冻结在原地，以获得额外的攻击机会。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">平安归来！ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/indiedev?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#indiedev</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/gamedev?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#gamedev</a> <a href="https://t.co/M7uTipAW6I">pic.twitter.com/M7uTipAW6I</a></p><p> — TriGear 团队 (@TeamTriGear) <a href="https://twitter.com/TeamTriGear/status/1701249245062529459?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 11 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>跑酷是<em>Mechabop</em>的另一个主要方面，它具有发射台和冲刺，可以让玩家智取敌人并快速穿越关卡的各个部分。</p><p> Rain 并不孤单，还会有<a href="https://twitter.com/i/web/status/1633150519903436801">Zeri</a>陪伴，Zeri 是一个戴着无檐小便帽的盒式磁带角色，可与<em>《塞尔达传说：时之笛》中的 Navi 相媲美。</em></p><p> 《<em>塞尔达传说》</em>的影响在<a href="https://twitter.com/TeamTriGear/status/1628439482419773440" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pokari</a>中也很明显，这是一个“销售独特商品的移动自动售货机机器人”，比如作为 Rain 的音箱左轮手枪弹药的特殊磁带。波卡里看起来很像<em>《梅祖拉的假面》</em>中首次出现的邮递员。</p><p>目前，尚不清楚该游戏的目标平台是什么，也不知道它何时会发布。然而，该团队的上一款游戏<em><a href="https://twitter.com/TeamTriGear/status/1527318161195941888" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《Contract Killer》</a></em>于 2022 年 5 月登陆 PC。</p><p> In other gaming news, a replica of <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/world-of-warcraft"><em>World Of Warcraft</em></a> &#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/world-of-warcraft-frostmourne-seized-during-drug-raid-by-canadian-police-3496706">Frostmourne was found in a police raid in Manitoba, Canada,</a> alongside nine firearms and over 130 grams of what was presumed to be crack cocaine.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/mechabop-is-a-rhythm-shooter-blend-of-hades-and-jet-set-radio-3496737">&#39;Mechabop&#39; is a rhythm shooter blend of &#39;Hades&#39; and &#39;Jet Set Radio&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 Matthew McConaughey's new book came to him “in a dream” like “a Bob Dylan ditty” https://www.nme.com/news/film/matthew-mcconaugheys-new-book-came-to-him-in-dream-bob-dylan-ditty-3496759?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=matthew-mcconaugheys-new-book-came-to-him-in-dream-bob-dylan-dittyAdam Starkey Tue, 12 Sep 2023 15:42:09 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3496759 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马修·麦康纳" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “That&#39;s how I think and dream, in song and rhythm”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/matthew-mcconaugheys-new-book-came-to-him-in-dream-bob-dylan-ditty-3496759">Matthew McConaughey&#39;s new book came to him “in a dream” like “a Bob Dylan ditty”</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马修·麦康纳" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Matthew-McConaughey-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Matthew McConaughey has revealed the origins behind his debut children&#39;s book, saying the idea came to him “in a dream”.</p><p> The actor&#39;s first ever picture book is released today (September 12), which matches rhyming couplets starting with the titular words “Just Because” to illustrations by Renee Kurilla.</p><p> Speaking to <a href="https://eu.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/books/2023/09/12/matthew-mcconaughey-just-because-interview-book-banning-parenting/70615773007/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>USA Today</em></a> about how the book came about, McConaughey said: “This book came to me in a dream. It was like a folk-song ditty. I woke up at 2:30 and just went and wrote it down. I thought it was a <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-dylan">Bob Dylan</a> ditty, which it kind of is.</p><p> “That&#39;s how I think and dream, in song and rhythm.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Just Because by Matthew McConaughey |书预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dlUJPFl3JUg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> One example of a couplet from the book reads: “Just because I forgive you, doesn&#39;t mean that I still trust. There&#39;s what you do, there&#39;s what I do, and yours is not my must.”</p><p> Explaining the concept further, McConaughey added: “It&#39;s about the poetry of life, instead of having the pressure on us that feels like we&#39;re told every day that we need to be absolute about every single thing. That&#39;s not really life. Life&#39;s much more poetic, odd, ironic. Once you admit all these contradictions, life becomes much more of a poem.”</p><p> This is the second book McConaughey has penned following his 2020 memoir <em>Greenlights</em> , which topped <em>The New York Times</em> non-fiction bestseller list.</p><p> Earlier this year, it was announced McConaughey would star in upcoming thriller <em>The Rivals Of Amziah King</em> from writer-director Andrew Patterson. He&#39;s also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-mcconaughey-is-getting-his-own-yellowstone-spin-off-3425815">set to lead an upcoming <em>Yellowstone</em> spin-off</a> .</p><p> McConaughey recently provided the voice of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-presley">Elvis Presley</a> in Netflix&#39;s adult animated sitcom <em>Agent Elvis</em> , alongside Kaitlin Olson and Johnny Knoxville.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/matthew-mcconaugheys-new-book-came-to-him-in-dream-bob-dylan-ditty-3496759">Matthew McConaughey&#39;s new book came to him “in a dream” like “a Bob Dylan ditty”</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
